DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(5,7,2);
$b = random(2,9,2);
$e1 = random(3,9,1);
$e2 = $e1 - 1 ;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \($a y^{$e1}+ y^{$e2}\). Your answer can be written as
\(y^a(Ay^b+B)\) where $BR
\(a\) equals: \{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $e2;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $a;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(b\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $e1-$e2;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
